These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, plum, spinach
3 different games are played: monopoly, domino, chess
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, family, animation
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: sunflower, balloon-flower, aconite
There are 3 different nationalities: colombian, german, italian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: tennis, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's sport is tennis is the german##1
 2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person watching animation movies##1
 3. the person drinking soy-milk is between the italian and the person drinking mirinda##2
 4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the colombian##1
 5. the person watching family movies is the person eating spinach##1
 6. the person playing chess is the colombian##1
 7. the person playing chess is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
 8. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
10. the person playing domino is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk   | 7up           |
| Food          | plum       | spinach    | lemon         |
| Game         | domino    | chess  | monopoly        |
| Movie-Genre           | musical | family   | animation      |
| Flower   | balloon-flower        | aconite    | sunflower       |
| Nationality   | german     | colombian  | italian       |
| Sport         | tennis     | water-polo | weightlifting |

