.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, juice, sprite
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
3 different games are played: billiard, domino, poker
City: nizza, marseilles, rome
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, british, dutch
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, puzzles, fishing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, water-polo, weightlifting
 1. the person who's hobby is fishing is the british##1
 2. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person playing poker##1
 3. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 4. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##2
 5. the dutch is on the far left##1
 6. the person drinking juice is the person traveling to nizza##1
 7. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the person playing billiard##1
 9. the person playing poker is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea   | sprite    | juice         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| Game   | billiard  | poker  | domino     |
| City   | rome       | marseilles      | nizza         |
| Nationality   | dutch      | british   | australian    |
| Hobby           | camping        | fishing      | puzzles         |
| Sport         | water-polo | baseball  | weightlifting |

