The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, pop, r&b
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea, aconite
The people have 3 different jobs:  entrepreneur, electrician, musician
City: hannover, boston, venice
 1. the person eating kale is the electrician##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person eating peas##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the electrician##1
 5. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who growsazalea and the fan of r&b##2
 8. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 9. the electrician is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
10. the musician is on the right of the person eating kale##1
11. the person who growsazalea is the person eating peas##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Food          | peas      | kale      | cabbage      |
| Hobby         | fishing   | skydiving | magic-tricks |
