 5. the fan of country is between the modern house and the person who's birthday is in may##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 7. the fan of country is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 8. the musician is the person eating blueberry##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in july is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

