 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is in the middle##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is in the middle##1
 3. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
 6. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person who likes green##2
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who growsballoon-flower is the person driving the subway##1
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the aristoff-smoker##1
11. the person driving the subway is the person who likes green##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | fanta      | tea      |
| Hobby         | drawing     | hiking     | singing  |
| Flower   | daffodil | marigold  | balloon-flower |
| Color   | lavender  | chestnut     | green |
| Cigar           | davidoff        | montecristo | aristoff     |
| Sport         | handball    | water-polo | soccer   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

