.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, november
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, pumpkin
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, hiking, singing
3 different games are played: backgammon, mah-jongg, snooker
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, augustsy, mystery
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, surfing, water-polo
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, bellflower, amaryllis
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person who growsamaryllis is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
3. the person eating mango is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person who's sport is rugby is between the person watching epic movies and the person playing mah-jongg##2
5. the person eating pumpkin is between the person playing snooker and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person eating pumpkin##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
9. the person watching augustsy movies is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Birthday      | august      | october      | november       |
| Food          | mango      | pumpkin    | broccoli   |
| Hobby         | singing    | baking     | hiking     |
| Game           | mah-jongg    | backgammon | snooker   |
| Movie-Genre   | augustsy    | mystery    | epic       |
| Sport         | water-polo | rugby      | surfing    |
| Flower     | bellflower       | daisy | amaryllis |

