.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
City: boston, colone, nizza
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, february, september
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, photography, reading
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, scientific, superhero
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, jazz, reggae
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, ice-hockey, snowboarding
3 different games are played: chess, bridge, domino
1. the person playing bridge is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person playing domino##1
5. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the fan of reggae##1
7. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of jazz##1
8. the person playing chess is the person watching superhero movies##1
9. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| City      | nizza       | boston     | colone         |
| Birthday          | june     | february      | september     |
| Hobby         | photography | reading    | cooking      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation   | scientific | superhero    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz        | reggae     | electronic   |
| Sport         | cricket     | ice-hockey | snowboarding |
| Game     | bridge     | domino       | chess    |

