.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: western, musical, zombie
City: boston, hannover, prague
The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, french, italian
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: january, september, august
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, roller
1. the person watching western movies is the person traveling to prague##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in january##1
3. the dressmaker is between the person watching zombie movies and the owner of the rabbit##2
4. the canadian is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
5. the owner of the dog is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
7. the fisherman is the person traveling to boston##1
8. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
9. the french is between the person traveling to boston and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | musical    | western       | zombie      |
| City          | boston   | prague   | hannover  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Nationality   | canadian   | french     | italian  |
| Pet           | rabbit     | dog        | hedgehog |
| Birthday         | september | january   | august  |
| Transport     | jet-ski    | roller     | car      |

 